Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=8}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You've had a serious look\Non your face for a while.{OG}{You've had a grim look\Non your face for a while now. - WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, I hope it's just my imagination. - OG}Well, I might just be\Nimagining things, but...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is? - OG}But what?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:20.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I feel like this ship hasn't been moving at all for a while. - OG}I feel like the ship\Nhasn't moved in a while.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:25.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:30.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, the sail isn't catching any wind at all... - OG}Now that you mention it,\Nthe sail isn't catching any wind...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dammit...! - OG}Oh no...!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We've entered the Calm Belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:38.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Charm Belt? - OG}{The Palm Belt? - Gab, "Charm" is a bit too far from "Calm" in English}The Balm Belt?{Rabbit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:39.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What the heck is that? - OG}The heck is that?{Gab, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Calm Belt! It's an area of sea where nothing moves a muscle! - OG}The {\i1}Calm{\i0} Belt! A sea where\Nnothing moves a muscle!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami grew her muscles? - OG}{You grew some muscles? - Gab}You grew some muscle?{Rabbit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! - OG}No, you idiot!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What was that? An earthquake? - OG}Was that an earthquake?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Earthquake? On the sea? - OG}An earthquake? But we're at sea.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You guys, enough chit chat! - OG}Come on, guys, focus!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fold the sails and start paddling now! - OG}{Fold the sails and start paddling! - Gab}Hoist the sails and start paddling!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Put the ship back on its earlier path! - OG}Put the ship back on course, now!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay, Nami-san! - OG}As you wish, Nami!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are you panicking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Paddling? This is a sailboat. - OG}And why paddle? This is a sailboat.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's right. - OG}Yeah, why?{Gab}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why're we taking the trouble to go back to where the Navy is waiting for us? - OG}Why bother when\Nthe Marines are back there?{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just do what I say! We're in big trouble! - OG}Just shut up and do as I say!\NWe're in big trouble!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, the sea is quiet. - OG}{But it's all nice and quiet here. - Gab}But the sea is nice and quiet here.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:15.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right, fine! Then I'll explain it for you! - OG}Alright, fine! I'll explain!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:23.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Listen. Since we rushed and ran away, we came further south than we planned! - OG}{Listen. Since we were in such a hurry,\Nwe went further south than planned! - Gab}Listen. Since we were in such a hurry,\Nwe went farther south than intended!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:25.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then did we enter the Grand Line? - OG}So we're in the Grand Line now?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If it was that easy,\Nanyone could enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look. - OG}Look here.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:37.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Grand Line is running between two sea areas! - OG}{The Grand Line runs\Nbetween these two areas. - Gab}The Grand Line runs between\Nthese two strips of sea.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:42.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you get it? The area on both sides of it is called the Calm Belt. - OG}{Are you following? The two areas\Nare called the Calm Belts. - Gab}Are you following? The two strips\Nare called the Calm Belts.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:47.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The reason is unknown but in these areas, there's no wind and no current. - OG}The reason's unknown, but no wind\Nor currents flow through them.{Gab+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're an area of sea with complete calm. - OG}{The sea there is completely calm. - Gab}These seas are completely calm.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sailboats run by catching winds, so it's an extremely dangerous area, - OG}{Sailboats run by catching wind,\Nso it's very dangerous, - Gab}Sailboats need wind to move\Nso it's very dangerous—{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{indeed, a fatal area, for them! - OG}{maybe even [/i1]fatal[/i0], for them! - Gab}{maybe even [/i1]fatal[/i0], for them! - Gab}maybe even {\i1}fatal{\i0}—without it!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, did you get it? - OG}Did you get all that, Luffy?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. At least that we're in trouble. - OG}Yeah. Basically, we're in trouble.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:00.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I see. Good, you got\Nmore than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So this is what the geezer meant when he said it was dangerous... - OG}So that's why the geezer\Nsaid it was dangerous...{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No wonder there hasn't been any wind. - OG}That explains the lack of wind.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can't do anything if the ship doesn't move. - OG}{Well, we can't do anything\Nif the ship can't move. - Gab}Not much we can do\Nif the ship can't move.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can just wait until the wind starts blowing. - OG}{Let's just wait until wind starts– - Gab}Can't we just wait for wind to–{PP+Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:14.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Like I said, once you're in this area, wind never blows no matter how long you wait! - OG}{I just explained this! Wind won't blow\Nno matter how long you wait in here! - Gab}I just explained this! Wind won't blow\Nno matter how long you wait here!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's another reason that people call this area dangerous! - OG}There's another reason\Nthis area is dangerous!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In this area... - OG}The Calm Belt is–{Gab, making the connection to 04:39 more obvious}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Calm Belt is the nest\Nof the sea kings. - OG}The Calm Belt is a nest of sea kings.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Moreover, the ones here are super huge! - OG}{And the ones here are especially big! - Gab}Specifically colossal ones.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:46.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're another reason why people can't cross the Calm Belt. - OG}They're the other reason people\Ncan't cross the Calm Belt...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What're we gonna do now? - OG}What do we do now?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They'll probably go back into the sea eventually. - OG}They'll go back into\Nthe sea eventually.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then we'll paddle hard using our oars. - OG}{When they do, we need\Nto paddle as hard as possible. - Gab}When they do, we paddle\Nas hard as possible.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}{Idiot! - OG}Shut it, idiot!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you do that... - OG}If it does that...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's gonna sneeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Amazing! I feel like we're flying! - OG}Wow! It feels like we're flying!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:25.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i0} flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like we're back on our original course... - OG}Looks like we're back on course...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We should be seeing the Red Line at any time now... - OG}We should be seeing\Nthe Red Line any moment now.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Grand Line, at last! - OG}{We're finally at the Grand Line! - Gab}Are we finally going\Ninto the Grand Line?!{PP+Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:46.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Sanji! We're finally going! We're finally going! - OG}Hey, Sanji! We're here,\Nwe're here, we're finally here!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sowwy! - OG}Sorry...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.41,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.66,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're here, we're here!{Added - Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.66,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.29,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're here, we're here, we're here!{Added - Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.29,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{is it really like how it's drawn here? - OG}is the drawing an accurate\Nrepresentation of what we'll find?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.42,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Stop that! - OG}Quit it!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:09.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'd heard the rumors about it,\Nand it's drawn on this map, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:13.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If it really is true, then the entrance to the Grand Line is a mountain! - OG}{If this is true, then the entrance\Nto the Grand Line is a mountain! - Gab}If all of that is true, then the entrance\Nto the Grand Line is a mountain!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We gotta crash into a mountain? - OG}{Do we have to run into it? - Gab}We gotta crash into it?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You can't be serious. - OG}You're kidding, right?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:22.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I didn't believe it myself, but the map\Nhas canals that lead to the mountain. - OG}{I was suspicious myself, but the map\Nshows canals leading to the mountain. - Gab}I doubted it myself, but the map\Nshows canals leading to the mountain.{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That might mean we have to go up it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Neat! - OG}Cool!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:33.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if there are canals or whatever, a ship can't climb up a mountain! - OG}Even with canals or whatever,\Na ship can't climb up a mountain!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But that's what the map says!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:38.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Nami-san would never say anything that's wrong! - OG}{Just listen to her! Nami would\Nnever say anything wrong! - Gab}Exactly! Nami would never\Nsay anything wrong!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You stole that map\Nfrom Buggy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Can we really trust it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Someone help with the rudder! - OG}{Someone help me move the rudder! - Gab}Someone help me move the whipstaff!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji{-kun}! Give Usopp a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't think with all his shouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Nami-san! - OG}Right away, Nami!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay! - OG}Here I go!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.51,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,It won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.39,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,It won't move! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,D-Doesn't this current\Nseem a bit strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Usopp! What did you just say? - OG}Usopp, say that again!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"D-Doesn't this current\Nseem a bit strong?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Current...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's what? - OG}What's it?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They really do go up the mountain! - OG}The canals {\i1}do{\i0} go up the mountain!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you still saying that stuff?! - OG}You're still on that?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The guiding light was\Ndefinitely pointing to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{on the Red Line... Reverse Mountain! - OG}Right on the Red Line:\NReverse Mountain!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Little help over here! - OG}Hey! What do I do now?!{PP+Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,See these canals here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:28.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If major currents from the four oceans all flow toward this mountain... - OG}If major currents from the four seas\Nall flowed toward this mountain...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:34.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then the four currents would go up\Nthese canals, collide at the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and then flow into the Grand Line! - OG}and flow into the Grand Line!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Reverse Mountain is a winter island,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:44.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so any currents that collide into the Red Line will plummet from the surface into the depths. - OG}so any currents that collide with\Nthe Red Line will go into the depths.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If we screw up and miss\Nthe entrance to the canal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{the [/i1]Going Merry[/i0] will run smack into the Red Line's rock face... - OG}{\t(2316,0,1,\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&HFDFEFD&\4c&HFDFEFD&)}the {\i1}Going Merry{\i0} will crash\Ninto the Red Line...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and get wrecked! - OG}{\t(1230,0,1,\c&HFEFEFC&\3c&HFEFEFC&\4c&HFEFEFC&)}and get completely wrecked!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:58.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And then we'd be at the bottom of the ocean. Understand? - OG}{And then we'd be at\Nthe ocean floor. Understand? - Gab}Then we'd end up at the bottom\Nof the ocean. Get it?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Interesting! - OG}Oh, {\i1}very{\i0} interesting!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So, basically, it's a mystery mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:07.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, maybe you don't get it... - OG}Well, I guess you wouldn't...{PP+Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Anyways, now that\Nwe're on this current, - OG}All in all, now that\Nwe're on this current,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{as long as we don't mess up with the rudder, - OG}{as long as we don't mess up, - Gab}as long as we steer correctly,{Gab+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:15.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we should be able to go straight to the summit of Reverse Mountain! - OG}it's a straight shot to the summit\Nof Reverse Mountain!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san! You're so amazing! - OG}You're amazing, Nami!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've never heard of ships going over mountains before. - OG}I've never heard of someone\Ngoing up a mountain by boat.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've heard some stuff before! - OG}I've heard some stories!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stories about the mystery mountain? - OG}About the mystery mountain?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:30.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I heard that half of everyone who heads to the Grand Line dies before entering it... - OG}{\q2}I heard that half of everyone who heads\Nto the Grand Line die before entering...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I knew getting in wouldn't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji{-kun}! Could you get the sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Nami-san! - OG}Of course, Nami!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I see the mystery mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Wh-What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Th-That's insanely huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So that's the Red Line, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:11.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I-I-I can't see the top because of the clouds! - OG}{Th-The t-top is so high up\Nthat it's covered by the clouds! - Gab}Th-Th-The t-top's all the way\Nabove the clouds!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're getting sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold the rudder good! - OG}Hold the rudder tight!{Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're on it! - OG}– On it!\N– On it!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nami! Wh-Where's the entrance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna crash into the rocks if we keep going this way! - OG}We're gonna crash\Nif we keep going this way!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The crack in that cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Keep going straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A-Are you serious?! - OG}Are you sure?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami! Is that the canal entrance? - OG}Nami! Is that the entrance?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This can't be for real! - OG}I can't believe this...!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:15.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The damn ocean really {\i1}is{\i0}\Nflowing up the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We gotta make our way through those water gates just right! - OG}We gotta be careful sailing\Nthrough those gates!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Otherwise the ship'll be busted into pieces! - OG}If we don't get it just right,\Nthe ship is done for!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{W-We're getting off course! More to the right! Right! Right! - OG}W-We're a little off!\NMore to the right! The right!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The right?! Go starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– The rudder!\N– The rudder! - OG}– The whipstaff!\N– The whipstaff!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Grab on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– We made it!\N– We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now it's just a straight\Nshot to the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Awesome, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're in the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Awesome! - OG}So cool!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're above the clouds now! - OG}Now we're {\i1}above{\i0} the clouds!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look! The summit! It's the summit! - OG}Look! It's the summit! The summit!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest sea in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{The One Piece is up ahead, somewhere! - OG}{The One Piece is somewhere in there! - Gab}The One Piece is somewhere up ahead!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:10.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you just hear something? - OG}Did you hear that just now?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Isn't it the wind? - OG}Wasn't it just the wind?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There must be lots of unusual landforms! - OG}{I can't wait to see\Nall of the unusual landforms! - Gab, is she saying something like this or more like "unusual landforms will lead to unusual wind"}{It must be from all the weird\Nterrains around here. - PP, the latter}It must be from all the weird\Nlandforms around here.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}! I see a mountain up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A mountain?! That can't be! - OG}A mountain?! That can't be right!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But it's really there! - OG}But there's really one there!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:51.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{After passing the Twin Capes up ahead, there should be nothing but ocean! - OG}It should be open sea once\Nwe pass the Twin Capes up ahead!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's not a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:03.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a black wall! - OG}It's a big black wall!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, it's not! - OG}No, it's not! That's...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then, what is it?! - OG}What is it then?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{a whale! - OG}It's a whale!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-Wh-What're we gonna do?! - OG}Wh-Wh-What are we g-gonna do?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Shall we fight? - OG}We should fight it!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! There's no way we can fight that! - OG}Are you crazy?! How are\Nwe gonna fight {\i1}that{\i0}?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{B-B-B-B-But, our path is blocked! - OG}B-B-But, i-i-it's blocking our way!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:27.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If it looks like a wall from this close, then where are its eyes?! - OG}If it looks like a wall from\Nthis close, where are its eyes?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:31.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right! It's possible that he may not have noticed us! - OG}That's right! Maybe it\Nhasn't noticed us yet!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But unless we do something, we'll run into it! - OG}{Either way, we gotta do\Nsomething before we crash! - Gab}Either way, we're about\Nto crash into it!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! We can get through on the left! - OG}Hey! There's an opening on the left!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Port! Hard to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But the rudder is broken! - OG}But the whipstaff is broken!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do something! I'll help, too! - OG}Well, figure something out! I'll help!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't work! - OG}This isn't working!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ship doesn't turn! - OG}The ship won't turn!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is this it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1175,1053)}{Cannon?! - OG}The cannon?!{Gab, is this effect too much lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(840,27)}{Cannon?! - OG}The cannon?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,1053)}{Cannon?! - OG}The cannon?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(270,27)}{Cannon?! - OG}The cannon?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! Did it stop? - OG}{Nice! Did it stop? - Gab}Alright! Did it stop?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're screwed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This might be it... - OG}Yeah, this is it...{Gab, making the repetition from 15:23 seem intentional :P}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,My special seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:56.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{get out of here before it's too late! - OG}Let's book it while we still can!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did he not notice the cannon attack because his body's too big?! - OG}Is it so big that\Nit didn't even feel it?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Or is it just slow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:06.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who knows?! Anyway, let's get out of here now! - OG}Who cares?! Let's get\Nthe hell out of here!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{My ears hurt! - OG}My ears!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Paddle! Just paddle!! - OG}Paddle! Just keep paddling!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We have to get away from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:30.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do\Nto my special seat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dumbass! - OG}– You dumbass!\N– You dumbass!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How was that?! Bring it on, you bastard! - OG}How was that, huh?!\NBring it on, you bastard!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Shut up already, you idiot!\N– Shut up already, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They've all been eaten... - OG}They all got eaten...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey you! Spit them out! Give everyone back to me! - OG}Hey, you! Spit them out!\NGive everyone back!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Spit them out! I'm saying give them back! - OG}Spit them out already! Listen to me!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You... You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're diving into the water, aren't you?! Stop it! - OG}Are you diving?! Stop it!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! I'm telling you to stop! Hey! - OG}Hey! I said stop! Hey!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please wait! Give my friends back! - OG}Please, stop! Give my friends back!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I said stop it! - OG}Stop it already!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna go on adventures together! - OG}We were just about\Nto go on an adventure!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're precious to me! - OG}I can't lose them!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:15.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do you think? - OG}So, what do you think?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What do I think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How [/i1]should[/i0] I think? - OG}What {\i1}should{\i0} I think?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-H-H-H-How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:48.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I was sure that we were swallowed by the whale... - OG}We were definitely\Nswallowed by that whale...{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's probably a dream. - OG}Yeah, it's gotta be a dream.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:02.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then, what are the island\Nand house doing there? - OG}{Then what's that island\Nand house doing there? - Gab}{Then what about\Nthat island and house? - Gab}Then, how do you explain\Nthat island and house?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They must be illusions. - OG}Hallucinations.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then this is... - OG}So, that's also...?{PP+Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– ...a Great King Squid!\N– ...a Great King Squid! - OG}{– It's a great king squid!\N– It's a great king squid! - PP+Gab}– It's an imperial squid!\N– It's an imperial squid!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like there's at least someone there. - OG}{Looks like someone's in there. - Gab}{Looks like a human lives here. - PP, it should say sth like human/person, to match sanji's response to it}Looks like someone lives there.{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I hope it's really a person... - OG}{I hope they're human... - Gab}Let's hope they're human.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I've had enough. I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:46.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy went somewhere, too. What's gonna happen to us? - OG}Luffy's gone, too...\NWhat's gonna happen to us?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, where's Luffy?! - OG}{Come to think of it, where [/i1]is[/i0] he?! - Gab}You're right! Where's Luffy?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What the heck is this? - OG}What the heck is all this?{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why is there a door and a passageway in a whale? - OG}{Why is there a door\Nand a hallway inside a whale? - Gab}Why is there a door\Nto a hallway inside a whale?{PP+Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sh-Sh-Sh-Shall we fire the cannon at that island?! - OG}Sh-Sh-Should we f-fire\Nthe cannon at that island?!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming out...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=9}===============================DIALOGUE============================
